觸多咗indie band ，就發覺音樂唔應該係咁單一，唔係ballad就電音，應該要有更多變化<br />\n可能韓國都有出色嘅indie band我唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人好鐘意math rock，喺一首歌入面可以有幾種唔同嘅曲風，好有趣，聽親都有驚喜<br />\n如果你接觸多啲唔同類型嘅音樂，會發現音樂可以有好多可能性，而唔係只係得普通情歌同埋電音舞曲，你會覺得其實kpop真係冇乜特別令人著迷嘅點，除咗啲明星個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23255813172f9cc7d2efe0081abb2dcc6a792754","tid":89334,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n連嘈交都搬d垃圾出黎，<br />\n香港大把indie band屌打泡菜la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實韓國都有好多有心做音樂嘅人 點解唔可以用一個欣賞嘅態度而要用一個比較嘅行為嚟看待音樂 未去真正聽過就話嗰樣唔好依樣唔好 依樣叫盲反呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哈，我就係識欣賞音樂先知咩野有質素，<br />\n聽完，好普通，<br />\nchord 底普通, arrangement薄，<br />\n用三和弦既diatonic野，配d咁普通既編曲，你話有咩值得聽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱，識音樂嘅都識作"},{"pid":"8082fcb7d593a4631326afb59cfe2156d0e73657","tid":89334,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"一堆臭雞"},{"pid":"b42d0513ed3ea76e71286e2435295594ec3b7e32","tid":89334,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"276b4be64a7ddfa1e634694e733f4422b66e5bcd","tid":89334,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哈<br />\n諗起琴日有條柒頭話一首咩野生花完勝香港所有歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲話韓國係街求期執件屌打張學友添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a81b17c4af771e5c209ce8738df8310d009ca4","tid":89334,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcb8057d5f31ce75176944d4e5dffc12cc0f52b5","tid":89334